- title "Moocs"
.mooc-quote
  %span.quote-icon= fa_icon 'quote-left 2x'
  %span.quote
    Self-education is, I firmly believe, the only kind of education there is.
    %span.quote-footer.text-right â€“ Isaac Asimov
%p.mooc-intro
  The idea of MOOC(Massive Open Online Course) is absolutely awesome, I feel
  more comfortable and productive taking MOOCs than traditional courses.
  Participating in MOOCs is now one of my favorite online activities.
  Below is a list of MOOCs I finished in my spare time.
- @moocs.each do |platform, mooc_group|
  %h2= platform
  - mooc_group.each do |mooc|
    .row.mooc
      .col-md-2= date_string(mooc.finish_date, true).html_safe
      .col-md-7= link_to mooc.name, mooc.course_link
      .col-md-1= link_to 'Statement', mooc.statement_link
      - if current_user
        .col-md-2.pull-right
          %button.btn.btn-sm.btn-primary= link_to 'Edit', edit_mooc_path(mooc)
          %button.btn.btn-sm.btn-danger= link_to 'Delete', mooc, method: :delete, data: { confirm: 'Are you sure?' }
- if current_user
  %button.btn.btn-md.btn-primary
    = link_to 'New Mooc', new_mooc_path
